{
  "3239250": {
    "name": "Clover Reset",
    "steam_appid": 3239250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/96a4a005462e5f31eddb79e6577f77f0.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/96a4a005462e5f31eddb79e6577f77f0.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“甜度99％×惊喜1％”！？　 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇见的瞬间已然喜欢的青春百合文字游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/38fdb089e8741d55e9eb2400bc44d2df.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/38fdb089e8741d55e9eb2400bc44d2df.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/15c059c893375badc3ae2bfe7f0e1fc4.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/15c059c893375badc3ae2bfe7f0e1fc4.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >转动的命运齿轮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少女们重复着相遇与相恋――――。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「请问，你是否知道四叶草的花语呢？」 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是以位于神奈川县湘南的“湘南才华学园”为舞台，讲述在友情与爱情之间摇摆不定的少女们的青春故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/8bf8870a6207f1a16c1438aab497c757.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/8bf8870a6207f1a16c1438aab497c757.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span>位于神奈川县的高偏差值女子学校“湘南才华学园”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，「立花茉铃」与好友「早乙女真白」和「神宫寺清香」一起迎来了一个稍微特别的日子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那是她们与转校生「九条雫月」的相遇，这位转校生在初高中一贯制学校中显得格外少见。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是一个身姿优雅、端庄美丽的女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于茉铃来说，虽然是第一次见面，却有种似曾相识的感觉……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当茉铃带着雫月参观学校设施的时候，她们来到了学校楼顶的展望台。在那里茉铃找到了四叶草。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个学校里有着这样的传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >――如果在展望台找到四叶草并将其夹在学生手册内的话就能实现愿望――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（我想和她更加亲近……和她变得更加……）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抱着这样的愿望，茉铃将「偶然」发现的四叶草作为礼物送给了雫月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以此为契机，在真白和清香的协助下，茉铃与雫月的距离逐渐靠近……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「还是别再理我了。我讨厌总是被保护……！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「小雫月，我们应该是朋友吧？」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，两人之间产生了感情的裂痕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这其中，雫月所隐藏的一个“秘密”与茉铃过去的“心理阴影”有着深刻的关联。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四位少女的成长、互助和回忆，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >茉铃她们能否找到属于自己的四叶草（幸福）呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/3d5e01e6601579d210f9914ca908aba8.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/3d5e01e6601579d210f9914ca908aba8.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >软萌治愈系女孩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>立花　茉铃（Tachibana Marin）</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV:白砂沙帆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（出演作品例：『侦探已死』夏洛特·有坂·安德森、『夏日重现』小舟澪、『蔚蓝档案 -Blue Archive-』春日椿、『蕾斯莱莉娅娜的炼金工房 ～忘却的炼金术与极夜的解放者～』蕾斯娜・修特涅利希特等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/ba3fa9492c28405de7e60413fcd63fb9.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/ba3fa9492c28405de7e60413fcd63fb9.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：16岁（登场时）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：3月14日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血型：O型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「和大家在一起很开心呀」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格内向温和，不太擅长表达自己的意见，温柔而体贴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她拥有女孩般可爱的气质，因此受到朋友们的宠爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于擅长绘画，希望能进入美术大学，正在向美术社的老师学习，但也在犹豫是否应该去预备校。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从遇见了雫月，她内心深处的“某种东西”开始发生了变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >酷酷的美少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>九条 雫月（Kujyo Shizuku）</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV:高田忧希</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（出演作品例：『偶像活动』黑泽凛、『NEW GAME!』凉风青叶、『小林家的龙女仆』艾露玛、『偶像大师 · 灰姑娘女孩』依田芳乃、『崩坏：星穹铁道』停云、『蔚蓝档案 -Blue Archive-』才羽绿等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/6a562a34031610f6333cdd77c6688825.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/6a562a34031610f6333cdd77c6688825.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：16岁（登场时）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：6月25日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血型：B型 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「……虽然有点不太习惯、但如果是茉铃的话……可以哦」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她给人一种冷静且聪明的印象，但实际很不擅长表达自己的情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦下定决心，就会全力以赴，能够认真踏实地做好每一件事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她对未来没有特别的执着，但希望能努力工作，独立自主地生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >转校后，面对初次见面的茉铃，她似乎怀有复杂的情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平时冷静沉着的她，却在涉及茉铃的事情上显得意外地感情化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开朗活泼的氛围营造者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>早乙女　真白（Saotome Mashiro）</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV:桑原由气</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（出演作品例：『小林家的龙女仆』托尔、『平凡职业造就世界最强』月、「成神之日」成神空、『我被抓到贵族女校当“庶民样本”』汐留白亚等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/a9cc9544155eb5ee3496483cd2aa5a80.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/a9cc9544155eb5ee3496483cd2aa5a80.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：17岁（登场时）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：10月31日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血型：AB型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「大家一起去K歌吧！小清清是强制参加哦！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >积极开朗的氛围系女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要真白在场，气氛就能变得活跃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无法放任困扰或脆弱的人，热衷于照顾他人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高中毕业后，希望能去服装设计的专业学校。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但又怕因此变得忙碌而无法照顾家人，所以内心有些挣扎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她和茉铃自高中起相识，并迅速成了好朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以真白的话来说，「茉铃是柔弱美少女，让人有强烈的保护欲。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧♧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很擅长照顾人的大姐姐类型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>神宫寺　清香（Jinguji Kiyoka）</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV:芝崎典子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（出演作品例：『偶像大师 · 闪耀色彩』桑山千雪、『怪怪守护神』近石千里、『平凡职业造就世界最强』莉莉安娜·S·B·海利希、『八月的棒球甜心』塚原雫等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/c0bbb610baaf88172bc59c0fa6d70557.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/c0bbb610baaf88172bc59c0fa6d70557.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：17岁（登场时）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：4月2日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血型：A型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「今天是去练习钢琴的日子，我就先回去了」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是表里如一的领导型人才。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文武双全的优秀学生。视野开阔，拥有与年龄不太相符的成熟人生观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她给人一种严肃的氛围，但偶尔也显露出可爱的一面，比如有些傻乎乎的地方，以及对虫子和鬼怪的异常害怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢音乐，本打算能进入音乐大学，成为一名作曲家，但未能获得父母的许可。尽管如此，她仍在努力尝试说服父母。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她和真白是从小一起长大的好友，一直以来像保护妹妹一样守护着真白。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然很多人都憧憬她是大家的姐姐般的存在，但她本人似乎并不太有这样的自觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/8678636b3202be4bfe3540f4bf324860.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/8678636b3202be4bfe3540f4bf324860.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >采用Live2D动态角色系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过动态多彩的表现方式来展现角色的喜怒哀乐！渲染演出效果与表现力！增强沉浸感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/5b666a765a1479e5f84edf62b170e035.poster.avif?t=1748602026\" width=280 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/5b666a765a1479e5f84edf62b170e035.webm?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/5b666a765a1479e5f84edf62b170e035.mp4?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/e672b3143b607c205217f1c31fe8bf7c.poster.avif?t=1748602026\" width=280 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/e672b3143b607c205217f1c31fe8bf7c.webm?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/e672b3143b607c205217f1c31fe8bf7c.mp4?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/138ac138035352a5347037b52085210a.poster.avif?t=1748602026\" width=280 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/138ac138035352a5347037b52085210a.webm?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/138ac138035352a5347037b52085210a.mp4?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/2b4daa2e5172a3a13ad78ed556b35657.poster.avif?t=1748602026\" width=280 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/2b4daa2e5172a3a13ad78ed556b35657.webm?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/2b4daa2e5172a3a13ad78ed556b35657.mp4?t=1748602026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/c63c6be4f66ed05f7785ecfee5b0f70d.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/c63c6be4f66ed05f7785ecfee5b0f70d.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >企划・原案：vividX</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色设计・原画：くきは</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脚本：かほく麻緒</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背景：金子わゆ / チーサー</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计：花杜ゆのき</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：ShoichiroToko</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras/0f2a224620087c5baac558a8aeb4fb92.avif?t=1748602026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239250/extras_big/0f2a224620087c5baac558a8aeb4fb92.avif?t=1748602026 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「Clover Reset」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作曲・编曲・作词：ShoichiroToko</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演唱：白砂沙帆（立花 茉鈴）</p>",
